scene.message:
Mark: Oh? For all your{nl}
grumbling, you sure{nl}
showed up, didn't ya.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Uesugi's been blabbing{nl}
it everywhere. Says this'll{nl}
be the last time, too.{waitkey}

Today I'll get a good,{nl}
long look at you{nl}
screaming and crying.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Oho.{nl}
Now that's good to hear.{nl}
I'll observe closely too.{waitkey}{ret}Mark: That jerk!{nl}
Never does anything good!{nl}
What're you all laughing at!{waitkey}{clearbox}Forget it, forget it!{nl}
I'm not going!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Perfect timing,{nl}
Sonomura, {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{clearbox}Inaba says he's cancelling{nl}
his plans. A real shame,{nl}
truly.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Yay!{nl}
Chisato and everyone are{nl}
waiting outside!{waitkey}C'mon, let's go, everyone!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Nanjo, Reiji!{nl}
You'll pay for this!{waitkey}{ret}Reiji: Heh...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
That Sonomura - it's like{nl}
that whole ordeal never{waitkey}happened.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...What?{nl}
You still going on{nl}
about that?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Nothing{wait_fr:60}. I just{nl}
recalled the last thing{nl}
to come from the "Sphere{waitkey}of Calamity"... Now,{nl}
let's go, {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Heh heh heh~{nl}
You can talk big, but{nl}
only till today!{waitkey}{clearbox}Mark, I hear you're{nl}
super scared of heights?{nl}
You little pants-wetter!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Heh heh heh.{nl}
I heard it all from{nl}
your mom!{waitkey}And in sixth grade, no less!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: That old hag!{nl}
{wait_fr:88}Shut up!{waitkey}Way better than wetting{nl}
yourself in middle school!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Sixth grade, middle{nl}
school, same thing. Heh heh.{nl}
Today I'll get a good look{waitkey}at you wetting yourself!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: These two... Where{nl}
do they think they are?!{nl}
Ugh... my head hurts...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Perfect timing!{nl}
{ctl08:1}Maki!{waitkey}{clearbox}Mark here just can't wait{nl}
to ride the Free Fall -{nl}
he's itching for it!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: What's wrong?{nl}
Chisato and everyone are{nl}
waiting outside! C'mon!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: This'll be fun.{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Still, Maki... it's like that{nl}
whole ordeal never happened.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: What's that?{nl}
You're still on about that?{nl}
Mean as ever, aren't ya.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Nothing{wait_fr:60}. I just{nl}
recalled the last thing{nl}
to come from the "Sphere{waitkey}of Calamity"... Now,{nl}
let's go, {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{ret}
